item.title: Models?
item.dc:creator: @Rog3r Rog3r
item.description:
@Rog3r wrote:

Well, every item in the game originally has a model, but since the client uses the cache to grab most, we don’t need to have everything in the folder. (Probably true)

However since you are using the program metaseq, you will have to download the files for it, that contains every item.
There are some tutorials that will help you solve that problem in the Client Hacking section.
